headline: GoDaddy Inc. (GDDY): A Bull Case Theory
summary: We came across a bullish thesis on GoDaddy Inc. on slo capital’s Substack by Justin. In this article, we will summarize the bulls’ thesis on GDDY. GoDaddy Inc.’s share was trading at $96.09 as of February 10th. GDDY’s trailing and forward P/E were 16.57 and 12.48 respectively according to Yahoo Finance.
